metadata.name: MEMORY
metadata.description:
Few hours left for 2023 and I wanted to share my memory of 2022 with you all. The memory of every single smile, the memory of love, the memory of gm hugs, the memory of failures, the memory of support, the memory of friendship and the memory of my existence. 

It's really hard to imagine my web3 journey without you all. Sending you the biggest and tightest hug. 

Let's make 2023 big together. Wishing you all a very happy new year. Love you all to the moon and beyond. 

~Vish
